headline: ICLR Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat, Stock Rises at After-Market
summary: ICON's fourth-quarter 2024 earnings and revenues beat estimates as it manages to navigate a challenging transition period.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid DGX and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Quest has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 13% to $170.50 per share while the index has gained 9.4%.
